# 🧠 6️⃣ Synchronization (CRITICAL 🔥🔥)

---

## ❗ Problem (Race Condition)

```java
count++;
```

👉 Multiple threads → wrong result

---

## ✅ Solution: synchronized

```java
class Counter {
    int count = 0;

    synchronized void increment() {
        count++;
    }
}
```

---

## 🔥 Interview Point

👉 Ensures **only one thread at a time**

---

