# 🧠 8️⃣ Deadlock (VERY IMPORTANT 🔥)

---

## ❗ Definition

When two threads wait for each other → stuck forever

---

## 💻 Example Concept

```text
Thread1 → lock A → waits for B  
Thread2 → lock B → waits for A  
```

👉 Deadlock 💥

---

# 🧠 9️⃣ Thread Safety

👉 Code that works correctly in multi-thread environment

---

## 🔹 Thread-safe classes

* StringBuffer
* Hashtable
* ConcurrentHashMap

